{"text_id":33465,"tokens":["In"," our"," work",","," we"," presented"," a"," large"," acceptance"," scintill","ator"," detector"," with"," wavelength"," shifting"," fibre"," read","-","out",","," which"," was"," specifically"," designed"," for"," the"," search"," of"," eta","-","nucleus"," bound"," states","."," The"," detection"," of"," these"," bound"," states"," can"," provide"," valuable"," information"," about"," the"," interaction"," between"," mes","ons"," and"," nuclei",","," which"," is"," of"," great"," interest"," in"," the"," field"," of"," nuclear"," physics",".","The"," main"," idea"," behind"," our"," detector"," was"," to"," provide"," a"," high","-","efficiency"," and"," low","-","background"," detection"," system"," for"," eta"," mes","ons",","," which"," have"," a"," short"," lifetime"," and"," are"," often"," difficult"," to"," distinguish"," from"," background"," signals","."," The"," detector"," had"," a"," large"," active"," area"," of"," ","1"," m","\u00b2,"," which"," made"," it"," possible"," to"," detect"," multiple"," particles"," simultaneously"," and"," to"," better"," discriminate"," signals"," from"," backgrounds",".","The"," key"," methodology"," we"," used"," was"," the"," combination"," of"," scin","tillation"," and"," wavelength"," shifting"," fibre"," technology",","," which"," allowed"," the"," detection"," of"," both"," charged"," and"," neutral"," particles","."," The"," scin","tillation"," material"," provided"," the"," initial"," energy"," deposition",","," while"," the"," wavelength"," shifting"," fibre"," read","-","out"," system"," allowed"," for"," efficient"," light"," collection"," and"," signal"," transmission",".","Our"," results"," showed"," that"," the"," detector"," had"," a"," high"," detection"," efficiency",","," particularly"," for"," low","-","energy"," eta"," mes","ons",","," and"," a"," low"," background"," rate","."," The"," detector"," also"," had"," a"," good"," spatial"," resolution",","," which"," allowed"," for"," the"," identification"," of"," the"," origin"," of"," particles"," in"," the"," detector",".","Overall",","," our"," work"," provides"," a"," valuable"," contribution"," to"," the"," search"," for"," eta","-","nucleus"," bound"," states"," and"," highlights"," the"," potential"," of"," large"," acceptance"," scintill","ator"," detectors"," with"," wavelength"," shifting"," fibre"," read","-","out"," for"," nuclear"," physics"," research","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}